'''Create MySQL Server and Connect with C'''
- Instal mysql server
```
sudo apt-get install mysql-server
```
- Connect to Server
```
sudo mysql -u root -p
```
```
Enter Password;
```
Note: If you use sudo,password is blank so just press enter to login to database

- Start Creating a Database
```
	CREATE DATABASE databasename
	USE databasename
```

'''Intall C client'''
```
sudo apt-get install default-libmysqlclient-dev
mysql_config --cflags
mysql_config --cflags
```
- Compile file using 
```
gcc -o test  -L/usr/lib/mysql -lmysqlclient test.c
```